[I] Text editor for your terminal: easy, powerful and fast

[T] Fresh is designed for discovery. It features native UIs, a full Menu
[T] system, and a powerful Command Palette. With full mouse support,
[T] transitioning from graphical editors is seamless.

[U] https://github.com/sinelaw/fresh

[A] Noam Lewis
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

[C] extra/editor
[F] CROSS CUSTOM-LTO

[L] GPL
[V] 0.2.25

[D] 17542f42b4844600a5eff034e68177a637cdbd3c4a3197a9733ac6ca fresh-0.2.25.tar.gz https://github.com/sinelaw/fresh/archive/v0.2.25/

cargoinstopt=
atstage cross && hook_add postmake 5 "install target/${arch_target}/*/fresh $root$bindir"
atstage native && hook_add postmake 5 "install target/*/fresh $root$bindir"
[ "$SDECFG_LTO" = 1 ] && export CARGO_PROFILE_RELEASE_LTO=true || export CARGO_PROFILE_RELEASE_LTO=off
